author: Boopesh Mahendran
description:
Generate maps using the Google Maps API. 

Enter a place name or latitude and longitude and click Generate Map. It's that simple!

 You can also change the Map Type, Zoom Level and add Custom Styles.
releaseNotes:
1. Remove default API key and related code 
2. Add user-defined API key implementation 
3. Add application-persistent plugin settings to save JSON and API keys 
4. Minor UI cleanup and fix plugin name casing
name: Maps Generator
